Package: ergo-proxy-node
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6
Suggests: fail2ban, rrdtool
Maintainer: BlockHost <dev@blockhost.io>
Description: Lightweight Ergo P2P relay proxy
 Message-forwarding proxy for the Ergo P2P network. Connects to Ergo
 nodes as a peer, accepts inbound connections, and relays P2P messages
 between them. First IPv6-enabled Ergo network endpoint.
